# The actual Next.js app lives in diagramatix/. These root-level npm artifacts
# are STRAYS — leftovers from packages once installed here instead of in
# diagramatix/. They must never be committed, and untracked they flood the IDE's
# git view (~1600 node_modules files). Anchored with a leading "/" so this only
# matches the repo-root copies, NOT diagramatix/package.json (which is tracked).
/node_modules/
/package.json
/package-lock.json
